import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Card, CardContent, CardMedia, Button, Box } from '@mui/material';

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Box sx={{ 
        textAlign: 'center', 
        padding: '4rem 0',
        backgroundColor: '#000000',
        color: '#FFFFFF',
        borderRadius: '8px',
        marginBottom: '2rem'
      }}>
        <Typography variant="h2" component="h1" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
          Welcome to Coach Nation Afrika
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#FFFFFF', opacity: 0.9 }} paragraph>
          Transform your life with Africa's premier fitness coaches
        </Typography>
        <Button 
          variant="contained" 
          size="large" 
          href="/booking"
          sx={{ 
            backgroundColor: '#FF0000',
            '&:hover': {
              backgroundColor: '#CC0000'
            }
          }}
        >
          Book a Session Now
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardMedia
              component="img"
              height="200"
              image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/400x200/?african,fitness"
              alt="Personal Training"
            />
            <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
              <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                Personal Training
              </Typography>
              <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666' }}>
                Get personalized workout plans and one-on-one attention from our certified African trainers.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardMedia
              component="img"
              height="200"
              image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/400x200/?african,workout"
              alt="Group Classes"
            />
            <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
              <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                Group Classes
              </Typography>
              <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666' }}>
                Join our energetic African-inspired group sessions for motivation and community support.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardMedia
              component="img"
              height="200"
              image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/400x200/?african,nutrition"
              alt="Nutrition Coaching"
            />
            <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
              <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                Nutrition Coaching
              </Typography>
              <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666' }}>
                Get expert advice on nutrition with an African twist to complement your fitness journey.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Home;
